title: Vortioxetine
summary: Vortioxetine, sold under the brand names Trintellix and Brintellix among others, is a medication used to treat major depressive disorder.[6] Effectiveness is viewed as similar to that of other antidepressants.[6] In the United Kingdom, it is only recommended in people who have not improved sufficiently on two other antidepressants.[7] It is taken by mouth.[6]
